This package is licensed under the MIT License (below), and incorporates code
derived from the following MIT-licensed projects, whose license notices are
reproduced in full as required:

- vanilla-extract (https://github.com/vanilla-extract-css/vanilla-extract):
  this package is a port of `@vanilla-extract/integration` (and of the debug-ID
  transform of `@vanilla-extract/babel-plugin-debug-ids`) onto the rolldown
  toolchain, replacing its esbuild child compilation with rolldown and its
  babel AST pass with the oxc AST.
- mlly (https://github.com/unjs/mlly): the ESM/CJS syntax detection regexes
  are vendored from `mlly`'s `detectSyntax`.

